  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4 \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Notification issued by Railway Department regarding train service",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Railway Department has informed that the train service will not be operated in the areas under police curfew.",
        "A police curfew has been imposed as people prepare for a massive protest against the government tomorrow.",
        "Police have been enforced in Colombo North, Colombo South, Colombo Madhi, Nukegoda, Kelani, Negombo Police Divisions from 9pm tonight until further notice.",
        "It is noteworthy that the Railway Department has informed that the train service will not be operated in the areas under police curfew."
      ],
